# `drop/` is the maintainer-to-agent inbox — everything
# Aaron deposits is ephemeral and must NOT enter git history.
#
# Track only:
#   - README.md  (the protocol doc)
#   - .gitignore (this file)
#
# Everything else is ignored and absorbed-then-deleted per
# the protocol in README.md.

# Ignore everything in this folder ...
*

# ... then re-include the two tracked sentinel files.
!README.md
!.gitignore
